now formalised support of Credit Lyonnais is vitally important to our
objective of building this organisation, maintaining its improved
performance and renewing MGM's stature in our industry.'
For the full year, MGM reported a net loss before extraordinary items and
accounting changes of Dollars 236m, down from Dollars 347m, on revenues of
Dollars 936.7m, against Dollars 921.7m.
